{
  "stem": "7600.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father went to the Aus-- to the American Consulate and applied-- you had to apply for a visa, and they told you you need an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we wrote-- he promised my unc-- my great uncle-- I think he was a great uncle-- promised to find somebody to send us visas, which was a surprise to everybody, because they didn't think he was going to do it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, the letter came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said he couldn't get for all of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was too much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't have anybody rich enough, but he could get a visa for two people and maybe my father and me would go first.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was acceptable, so we-- we were sitting there hoping and hoping that he would send it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But somehow, it just never came until very, very late in 1937.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's when we found out that I could get a visa immediately because of the quota system.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was born in Vienna, but he was born in what was now Romania, and Romania had used up their quota system for a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a strict quota system in the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They allowed so many people from so many countries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And apparently the Eastern countries, like Poland, Romania, they used them up because a lot of people left there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he would have to wait a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we were sort of stymied, and we went into 1938.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now in March, 1938, Hitler took over Austria, and I remember that day very well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I came home from something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was already dark, late at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And somebody yelled at me, you lousy Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Your day has come.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
